(a) The model shall capture all relevant risk factors which materially influence the
NCCD contracts and reflect the nature, scale and complexity of the risks
inherent in the NCCD contracts;

(b) The model shall calculate an estimate of the potential future exposure of
NCCD contracts, based on a one-tailed 99 per cent confidence interval over
a 10-day time horizon;

(a) The model shall be subject to initial and periodical (at least once a year)
independent validation to validate its conceptual soundness and the
appropriateness of the model for the derivatives for which it is being used;
